        },
        {
          "id": "tldr-product:2025-12-23:a06",
          "order": 2,
          "title": "THE CHALLENGE OF SELLING CARE & FEEDING INVESTMENTS TO MONEY-SIDE EXECUTIVES",
          "summary": "Care and feeding work is hard to defend because it doesn't show up as immediate revenue. Treating R&D as a portfolio, not a feature list, is the only reliable way to protect long-term product health.",
