          "id": "tldr-product:2025-12-23:a07",
          "order": 1,
          "title": "THE PRODUCT MODEL AT GOOGLE",
          "summary": "Google's success comes from a product model that empowers teams to solve hard problems through continuous discovery, strong technical leadership, and outcome-driven execution. This approach has allowed the company to scale, dominate mature markets, and adapt effectively to major shifts like mobile and AI.",
          "url": "https://www.svpg.com/the-product-model-at-google/?utm_source=tldrproduct",
          "reading_time_minutes": 10,
          "source_domain": "svpg.com",
          "content_type": "editorial",
          "is_sponsor": false
        },
        {
          "id": "tldr-product:2025-12-23:a08",
          "order": 2,
          "title": "THE ODDS ARE AGAINST FINANCIAL SUPERAPPS",
          "summary": "Financial superapps fail when they optimize for short-term speculation instead of long-term trust. Products that increase churn may look profitable early, but weaken the business over time.",
